creator: Carvolution AG
descriptionHtml:
You wonder how many miles you have driven? With our app you can check it out anytime. Are you so excited about our service that you want to tell your friends about us? Please recommend Carvolution and our car subscription.
You try to remember where you left your car in a big car park? Let the app do it for you. You will easily find your car again.
Please get in touch with us through your app - we are happy to help. If you have a technical problem or are involved in an accident, your app is the fastest way to contact us or our insurance partner’s assistance. Your app keeps you updated about news, services and tyre changes - which you can schedule directly through the app.

We wish all our Carvolutioners a great and save journey. We would love to hear your feedback and suggestions - maybe our app will soon include your desired feature.
descriptionShort: The new app for clever drivers

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: You can now see your invoices in the app. It’s now easier to see how much kilometers you drove. Various bug fixes.

title: Carvolution | Car Subscription

creator: Carvolution AG
descriptionHtml:
Discover your new car in an all-inclusive bundle. Our mission is to offer you an all-round carefree package for your dream car. Simple, flexible and affordable.


With the Carvolution app, you have all the important information about your car subscription at a glance with ease and paperless. In the kilometre overview, you can find the kilometres you have driven so far and whether they match your selected kilometre package. This means you always have an overview of your kilometres and can make changes to your kilometre package as required, whether upwards or downwards.
You'll also find details of your insurance, information on tyre changes and services, and an overview of all your bills. If you want to report a claim, you can also do this conveniently via the app, without much hassle.


You will also find your personal recommendation code in the app, which you can send to your family, friends and other interested people, all of whom will benefit from attractive discounts.
